wah.giovann.csvhandler

Class CSVRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • wah.giovann.csvhandler.CSVRecord

  • public class CSVRecord
extends Object
    The CSVRecord class represents a row of data in a .csv file. An instance of of this class can only be created in the context of an existing CSVArray instance.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Giovann Wah
